Traylor Howard https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Traylor_Howard 0 Traylor Elizabeth Howard (born June 14, 1966) is an American actress. She is known for playing Sharon Carter on the television series Two Guys and a Girl, and Natalie Teeger on the USA Network series Monk.
